 of aircraft owned by the Mexican Government, among", "which is the preparation of a market study to identify potential bidders and estimate the market prices of", "aircraft based on preliminary estimates value.", "In this sense, people and companies interested in buying one or more aircraft, which are specified in the", "document attached to this invitation as to register and express their interest, accordance with the Annex 1,", "following procedure:", "\u2022 This invitation is open to national and foreign individuals and companies interested, who Participants:", "are interested in buying one or more aircraft included in (Note: This process is not open to Annex 1.", "press).", "\u2022 The interested in participating in this request for information (RFI) should download the Announcement:", "documents using the United Nations global portal for suppliers (UNGM) at the following link:", "https://www.ungm.org/Public/Notice/122731", "\u2022 The invitation will be valid since 27th February 2021 at 00:00 until 15th March 2021 at 23:59, Calendar:", "Mexican City local time.", "\u2022 Includes the following documents, which must be completed and sent to email, Documents:", "adquisiciones.mexico@unops.org:", "\u2714 Request for Information RFI/2021/002", "\u2714 \u2013 Annex 1 Aircraft List", "\u2714 \u2013 Annex 2 Privacy Statement", "\u2714 \u2013 Annex 3 Aircraft Description", "\u2714 \u2013 Annex 4 Request for Information", "\u2714 \u2013 Annex 5 Estimated Value", "Finally, all information received will be treated as strictly confidential and will be used only for the purpose", "of this process.", "Sincerely,", "UNOPS M\u00e9xico", "UNOPS M\u00e9xico www.unops.org", "Ave. F.C. de Cuernavaca # 76, Email:adquisiciones.mexico@unops.org", "Lomas de Chapultepec", "Ciudad de M\u00e9xico, M\u00e9xico", "CP 11000"], "bbox": [[0.680556, 0.076778, 0.08904999999999996, 0.017383], [0.774075, 0.075295, 0.027105999999999963, 0.018866], [0.805686, 0.076778, 0.08633299999999988, 0.0173